{"type": "article", "id": 29280, "title": "兼具救生衣功能的漂浮装置", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-07T23:03:26Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160707165914qkBtlKxhVyRGwINn.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>为了鼓励更多人能够安全地参与水上活动，来自波兰的 <a href=\"http://juliagrochal.allyou.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Julia Grochal</a> 设计了一款名为 IUW 的漂浮装置，可以当作可抛出的运动救生衣使用。IUW 的外层采用含有氯丁橡胶涂层的尼龙制成，这种材料不仅耐磨、防水、防紫外线，还有着不错的保温功能。内部使用了聚氨酯泡沫座位填充物，能塑造出更贴合人体的形状，同时提供足够的浮力，让人们在漂浮时也可以灵活行动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607071709201u960eXRt3OPfoVh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707170920xCnsiLdFQHW8UOlu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707170920bTXU1wSA3cVDJjN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.512225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707170920F9InxG0Y3LEyCpzw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.511002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}